'''Notes'''<br>
<small>10.{{note|j}} Ireland was originally scheduled to announce its votes as the 32nd country, but instead voted 42nd (last). The reason for this was technical difficulties in the minutes running up to the voting presentation.</small>

=== Commentators ===
Most countries sent commentators to [[Baku]] or commentated from their own country, in order to add insight to the participants and, if necessary, the provision of voting information.

